Torrents MultiSearch
============

This extension is for Chrome\Opera\Firefox, which can search on multiple trackers at once, without resorting to third-party search engines.


**Works as follows:**

You enter into a search query - extansion introduces your request on trackers which you are looking for and gives you the results on a single page.

**Main blog:**

http://bug-report-blog.blogspot.ru/2012/09/torrents-multisearch.html

